						<p><hi rend="bold">Date lost.</hi></p>						

						<p>Fragmentary. Forms the concluding portions of the record. Seems to refer to the sale of a piece of land for a flower garden to the deity. States that the record was ordered to be engraved on the wall called the Rājamahēndraṉ-tiruchchuṟṟumāḷigai.</p>						

